description:
Makeup artist Sir John took a break from creating Beyoncé's next earth-moving look to hang with us. We talk Lemonade, Insta-haters, and the summer beauty hack he swears by. But before that! Jenn's new tattoo, an SPF report card, and if wearing makeup can earn you more cash.
